Slide_Consko

Map by Skope.

This is a special slide map. You don't die if you crash into something (like in re_slide_)...
You got 4 minutes to finnish the Map. If nobody finnished it all Players will Teleport into a jail (every Player get's a knife).

If anyone finnished the Map he get a M249 and a Knife to kill the T's/CT's.

24 Players are allowed. (12 T's and 12 CT's)

WARNING: NoBlock is requierd for the Map! Or all players get stuck!


I hope you like my first slide Map!
